<blockquote>
  <blockquote>
    <p>instant-markdown-d is a small Node.js server that enables instant
compilation and previewing of Markup files.</p>

    <p>A plugin can easily be written for any text editor to interface with
it.</p>

    <p>One currently <a href="https://github.com/suan/vim-instant-markdown">exists for
Vim</a>.</p>
  </blockquote>

